<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Tenedos anchicaya sp. n. A−D. Male palp (IAvH-I-6113): A. Ventral view. B. Retrolateral view. C−D. Female epigynum (IAvH-I-6114): C. Ventral view. D. Dorsal view. Abbreviations: ApC, appendix of the conductor; C, conductor; CD, copulatory ducts FD, fertilization ducts; LB, lateral borders; MA, median apophysis; MFP, median field plate; pRTA, posterior branch of retrolateral tibial apophysis; S, spermathecae; SD, spermatic ducts;VTA, ventral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: A−D: 1 mm; E−F: 0.5 mm." ;
